# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:739
msgid ""
"**Usage Example:** Removing the initial portion of a clip to focus on a "
"specific scene or moment."
msgstr "**مثال کاربردی:** حذف بخش ابتدایی کلیپ برای تمرکز بر صحنه یا لحظه خاص."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:740
msgid ""
"**Tip:** Utilize the \"Start\" property in combination with the \"End\" "
"property for precise clip trimming."
msgstr ""
